{"tid":568591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人已經灰到盡頭 跌落谷底","createTime":"2018-02-22T02:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T06:09:35.000Z","uid":171409,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b66e38dfa966364a2c1f85a09337a634f7bba546","tid":568591,"uid":171409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"過年就係最灰既日子 個個開開心心 團團圓圓<br />\n而自己屋企就諸事不順  發生完一野樣<br />\n你捱過去之後 就會發生更大件事 不停loop<br />\n好快你會明白你有幾傷心 絕望 都係無補於事<br />\n身邊既人既關心問候都只會係一時半刻<br />\n地球一樣係咁轉 人一樣係咁生活<br />\n如果我有70歲命 寧願用20年命換番一段開心有錢，屋企整整齊齊既人生 <br />\n比我活多20年夠了.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c39002f40c863cb7290b3a4818af52e0376ef5","tid":568591,"uid":163849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"其實谷底先最爽<br />\n<br />\n因為之後無論你點樣行都一定係向上走"},{"pid":"4ea947fe0d63535a8125c4bf6488026672306781","tid":568591,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c39002f40c863cb7290b3a4818af52e0376ef5","tid":568591,"uid":163849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"其實谷底先最爽<br />\n<br />\n因為之後無論你點樣行都一定係向上走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"最爽既係衝到谷底任人踩嗰種快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8553022beb29b3b46610b5b8aee0a10548614a","tid":568591,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"覺得已經好低潮 唔敢諗到谷底未"},{"pid":"00094ba300d71d42412ef465353b97b23a1014eb","tid":568591,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df8553022beb29b3b46610b5b8aee0a10548614a","tid":568591,"uid":126977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"覺得已經好低潮 唔敢諗到谷底未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3490d23768ca53594616c6575963aa3d05ffe1","tid":568591,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"正所謂低處未算低，<br />\n人生同股票一樣屄，<br />\n你以為 10 蚊跌到 3 蚊係鐵底，<br />\n佢就跌到得返 5 毫子過你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人有錢有女有車有樓高大又靚仔，<br />\n佢個人仆街刻薄涼薄依然風光有氣勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有人冇錢冇女冇車冇樓出生盲又跛，<br />\n就算心地好到加零一依然係澼地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁你哋連巴連絲又點睇？<br />\n仲相信天理常存過人世？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31557b41da6c38570a9860fb575c8a445d629305","tid":568591,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c39002f40c863cb7290b3a4818af52e0376ef5","tid":568591,"uid":163849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"其實谷底先最爽<br />\n<br />\n因為之後無論你點樣行都一定係向上走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"可能成世都係谷底呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd84553848251e0ca8ccfaf8c0b549f5777edaa","tid":568591,"uid":170730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"琴晚跌左銀包 而家煩死<br />\n無八達通 無身份證 無卡禁銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1baaf0660e7ee529f13f4053a39e8300adb0d1","tid":568591,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31557b41da6c38570a9860fb575c8a445d629305","tid":568591,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c39002f40c863cb7290b3a4818af52e0376ef5","tid":568591,"uid":163849,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"其實谷底先最爽<br />\n<br />\n因為之後無論你點樣行都一定係向上走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"可能成世都係谷底呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n灰嘅人根本唔識咁諗"},{"pid":"5fcfcd0320084c1126da19eb0060c2e8d2a2cc39","tid":568